    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel delivery will start from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the last digit of the vehicle's registration number and the relevant date, fuel distribution will start tomorrow (21) across the country, Mr. Kumara Rajapaksa, the president of the Petrol Station Owners Association, said today (20) afternoon.",
        "Mr. Kumara Rajapaksa said that the 'National Fuel Licence' is not relevant for the distribution of that fuel and only vehicles with the last digit 3, 4 and 5 of the vehicle registration number should come to get fuel today.",
        "Ceylon Petroleum Private Tanker Association Joint Secretary D. V. In the inquiry made to Mr. Shanta Silva yesterday afternoon, he said that the tankers have not been called to report for fuel transportation until the afternoon.",
        "A senior official of the Ministry of Energy said that the Petroleum Corporation currently has a stock of nearly 80,000 metric tons of diesel and 35,000 metric tons of gasoline."
      ],
